---
import { siteConfig } from '../../config/site'
---

<section
  class="site-container pt-hero-top pb-section"
  aria-labelledby="hero-title"
>
  <ul
    class="flex list-none flex-wrap items-center gap-x-3 gap-y-2 p-0"
    aria-label="주요 직무"
  >
    {
      siteConfig.roles.map((role, index) => (
        <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
          {index > 0 && (
            <span
              class="size-1 rounded-full bg-site-accent"
              aria-hidden="true"
            />
          )}
          <span class="text-site-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] text-site-muted uppercase sm:text-site-sm">
            {role}
          </span>
        </li>
      ))
    }
  </ul>

  <h1
    id="hero-title"
    class="mt-8 text-site-hero-name leading-[0.95] font-extrabold tracking-[-0.045em] text-balance text-site-text"
  >
    {siteConfig.title}
  </h1>

  <p
    class="mt-6 text-site-hero-tagline leading-[1.05] font-light tracking-tight text-balance text-site-text/90"
  >
    Designing Interfaces,<br />
    Building <span class="text-site-accent">Experiences.</span>
  </p>

  <p
    class="mt-8 max-w-2xl text-site-base leading-relaxed text-pretty text-site-muted sm:text-site-lg"
  >
    온/오프라인 디자인, 웹퍼블리싱, 개발 프로젝트와<br
      class="hidden sm:block"
    /> 배움과 경험을 기록하는 개인 포트폴리오 아카이브 블로그.
  </p>

  <nav
    class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4"
    aria-label="소개 바로가기"
  >
    <a
      href="#design"
      data-smooth-anchor
      class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-site-pill bg-site-accent px-6 py-3 text-site-sm font-bold text-site-bg transition-colors duration-200 hover:bg-site-accent-strong"
    >
      작업 보기 <span aria-hidden="true">↓</span>
    </a>
    <a
      href="#about"
      data-smooth-anchor
      class="inline-flex items-center rounded-site-pill border border-site-border px-6 py-3 text-site-sm font-bold text-site-text transition-colors duration-200 hover:border-site-accent hover:text-site-accent"
    >
      소개
    </a>
  </nav>
</section>
